<hymn_number>76</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kalvari tang khu gal thil leu hing,
 I Lalpau in A thawkna chu mui tiu;
 A thisan luong haw leh a lu a linglukhuk,
 I gitloh ziek ahi maw tih chu he tai tiu.

[V2]
 I gitloh ziekin melma hiem,
 A thuok zo ngei maw!
 Ziebang lawma hehpihna hi,
 Kuomah cha'n a nei puou.

[V3]
 2. Ana na lawm lawm e Lalpa thawkna!
 Ka enchim thei puoi ka Lal thawkna chu;
 Melmate'n guolnawp bawlnan mang, Kalvari ah,
 Tawtbawlna'n a mang ui Roman sepaihte chun.

[V4]
 3. Ka hehpih hukdampan A thawkna chu,
 Hetngilh guol ei puoi, A dangchakna chu;
 Ngilh ni ka nei thei puoi lainat a um taluoi,
 Khawvel gitloh ziekin thihna haksa A thuok.

[V5]
 4. Kalvari tang khu en kit zel ingka,
 Ka enchim thei puoi ka Lal thawkna chu;
 Lungmuon ding nei ! loin ka Lalpa a um a,
 &quot;Aw, he pa! ei nusie kin&quot; tin A kiko hi.</lyrics>
<title>Kalvari Tang</title>
</song>